{
  "stem": "27.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Your political affiliation, who you know, do you know any underground thing, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those were taken out, and they were sent back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you could see how they looked, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They all beaten up, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The face was distorted, their teeth knocked out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember a very good friend of my father who was a lawyer, Dr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Miklos.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was taken out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he right away came to my father and said, if they take you out, Joe-- my father's name was Joe-- take you out, don't even-- tell them everything they want to hear and lie more.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tell them here and here, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because everybody, like us too, had hidden stuff, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we knew already they not take it away, so made a false wall in the basement.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where hidden stuff were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We hope when we come back, whoever going to come back going to find it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't find nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's-- [LAUGHS] we didn't even-- but who cares.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was a second thought.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But as far as death, you know, in the ghetto, except those exceptions-- and political mostly-- but taken out, you know what I mean, it was nothing, really.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was sure fire, because don't forget that the-- we were not four weeks after the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they started taking out right away, immediately.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Hungarian's gendarme, the other one-- they handled it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were just too busy with the movement of the transport than to worry about us who were stayed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every day they came out, and they had-- the-- there was a Jewish community in the ghetto who had to give them the list of every-- and every single person and child.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
